      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The equal suffrage convention\nwill convene tomorrow morning at\n$50 o'clock at the Masonic temple\n\n\nA large attendance Of delegates\nis expected, and a most interesting\nsession is assured. In the evening\nq dinner will be given at the\nchamber of commerce.\n\n\nMrs. Hutton, president of the\nSpokane Equal Suffrage club, said\nthat there will be a harmonious\nmeeting, and that she has heard\nOF no possible conflicts."
    }
